NAME
	build - documents for building things

DESCRIPTION
	These docs are coming up soon (in a few years):

		objects		General object document
		livings		Living functions for both players and monsters
		monsters	Monsters and NPCs
		players		Functions used with players only
		rooms		Rooms in general
		virtuals	Virtual rooms
		doors		Doors and keys
		weapons		Weapons
		armours		Armours and other worn things
		drinks		Drinks and drink containers
		containers	Bags, sacks etc.
		torches		Light sources
		foods		Foodstuff

	These docs are in directory /doc/man/man5

SEE ALSO
	armours, containers, doors, drinks, foods, livings,
	objects, players, monsters, rooms, torches, virtuals, weapons
